comments: Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Conley's (UTA) path.
Conley (UTA) places a hand on Morant's (MEM) side but does not extend or deliver any contact during Morant's driving shot attempt.
Allen (MEM) legally contests Bogdanovic's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Brooks (UTA) makes contact with the ball then marginal contact with Favors' (UTA) hand as they engage during the rebound.
Anderson (MEM) makes contact with the ball then marginal contact with Favors' (UTA) arm as he completes the dunk.
O'Neale (UTA) legally contests Brooks' (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Valanciunas (MEM) and Favors' (UTA) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Bogdanovic (UTA) establishes himself in a picking position in Morant's (MEM) path without delivering any contact.
As Bogdanovic (UTA) prepares to pass, he makes marginal contact with Morant (MEM).
Brooks (MEM) legally contests Conley's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Favors (UTA) legally contest Morant's (MEM) driving shot attempt.
As O'Neale (UTA) moves off ball, he delivers contact to Allen (MEM) that affects his ability to defend the play.
Brooks (MEM) does not make any contact with O'Neale (UTA) during his play at the basket.
Allen (MEM) makes clean contact with the ball during the rebound.
Favors (UTA) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Anderson's (MEM) path and does not deliver any contact.
Anderson (MEM) makes contact with Bogdanovic's (UTA) body during his jump shot attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) makes marginal contact with Allen's (MEM) arm as he dribbles.
Conley (UTA) makes contact with Morant's (MEM) wris prior to making contact with the ball.
Conley (UTA) makes contact with the ball during Morant's (MEM) driving shot attempt and Favors (UTA) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact from Morant once the ball is loose.
Anderson (MEM) commits a take foul on Bogdanovic (UTA).
Anderson (MEM) legally contests Bogdanovic's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Conley (UTA) makes marginal contact with Allen (MEM) as they engage during the rebound.
